t;pre&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>Q\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>R\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rp\"><code>&lt;rp&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rtc\"><code>&lt;rtc&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>S\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>已废弃:</strong> 该特性已经从 Web 标准中删除，虽然一些浏览器目前仍然支持它，但也许会在未来的某个时间停止支持，请尽量不要使用该特性。</p></div>\n<p>HTML marquee 元素（<code>&lt;marquee&gt;）</code> 用来插入一段滚动的文字。你可以使用它的属性控制当文本到达容器边缘发生的事情。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>警告：</strong> <code>&lt;marquee&gt;</code> 元素已经 <strong>过时</strong>，请不要再使用。尽管一些浏览器仍然支持它，但它不是必须的。此外，使用这个元素基本上是你可以对你的用户做最糟糕的事情之一，所以请不要这样做。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"behavior\"><a id=\"attr-behavior\" href=\"#attr-behavior\"><b><code>behavior</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置文本在 marquee 元素内如何滚动。可选值有 <code>scroll</code>，<code>slide</code> 和 <code>alternate</code>。如果未指定值，默认值为 <code>scroll</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"bgcolor\"><a id=\"attr-bgcolor\" href=\"#attr-bgcolor\"><b><code>bgcolor</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>通过颜色名称或十六进制值设置背景颜色。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"direction\"><a id=\"attr-direction\" href=\"#attr-direction\"><b><code>direction</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置 marquee 内文本滚动的方向。可选值有 <code>left</code>, <code>right</code>, <code>up</code> and <code>down。</code>如果未指定值，默认值为 <code>left</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>以像素或百分比值设置高度。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"hspace\"><a id=\"attr-hspace\" href=\"#attr-hspace\"><b><code>hspace</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置水平边距。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"loop\"><a id=\"attr-loop\" href=\"#attr-loop\"><b><code>loop</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置 marquee 滚动的次数。如果未指定值，默认值为 −1，表示 marquee 将连续滚动。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scrollamount\"><a id=\"attr-scrollamount\" href=\"#attr-scrollamount\"><b><code>scrollamount</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置每次滚动时移动的长度（以像素为单位）。默认值为 6。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scrolldelay\"><a id=\"attr-scrolldelay\" href=\"#attr-scrolldelay\"><b><code>scrolldelay</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置每次滚动时的时间间隔（以毫秒为单位）。默认值为 85。请注意， 除非指定 truespeed 值，否则将忽略任何小于 60 的值，并改为使用 60。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"truespeed\"><a id=\"attr-truespeed\" href=\"#attr-truespeed\"><b><code>truespeed</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>默认情况下，会忽略小于 60 的 scrolldelay 值。如果存在 truespeed，那些值不会被忽略。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vspace\"><a id=\"attr-vspace\" href=\"#attr-vspace\"><b><code>vspace</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>以像素或百分比值设置垂直边距。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>以像素或百分比值设置宽度。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件回调","title":"事件回调","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"onbounce\"><a id=\"attr-onbounce\" href=\"#attr-onbounce\"><b><code>onbounce</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当 marquee 滚动到结尾时触发。它只能在 behavior 属性设置为 alternate 时触发。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"onfinish\"><a id=\"attr-onfinish\" href=\"#attr-onfinish\"><b><code>onfinish</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当 marquee 完成 loop 属性设置的值时触发。它只能在 loop 属性设置为大于 0 的某个数字时触发。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"onstart\"><a id=\"attr-onstart\" href=\"#attr-onstart\"><b><code>onstart</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当 marquee 开始滚动时触发。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"start\">start</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>开始滚动 marquee。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"stop\">stop</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>停止滚动 marquee。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This text will scroll from right to left<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>up<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This text will scroll from bottom to top<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>down<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>solid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    This text will bounce\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/rendering.html#the-marquee-element-2","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.marquee"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.marquee","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"事件回调","id":"事件回调"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"HTML marquee 元素（<marquee>） 用来插入一段滚动的文字。你可以使用它的属性控制当文本到达容器边缘发生的事情。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<marquee>: The Marquee element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<marquee> : l'élément de fronton (obsolète)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<marquee>: マーキー要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<marquee>：捲動元素（已過時）","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/marquee","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/marquee/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee","title":"<marquee>"}],"pageTitle":"<marquee> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}